In response to the incident the anti-racism campaign group Kick It Out issued a statement praising Norwich fans for not tolerating the alleged abuse.

'Kick It Out praises Norwich City supporters for reporting an alleged racist incident which occurred in the away end during yesterday’s (10 August) fixture against Wolverhampton Wanderers at Molineux.

